meetube (0.8.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * 480p and 720p video via dual-stream playback — separate video and audio
    elementary streams demuxed on-device — alongside 360p progressive.
  * Subtitles: timed-text captions overlaid during playback, selectable per track.
  * Video seeking on progressive and dual streams.
  * More detailed loading status: connecting / buffering / seeking / demuxing
    phases with a live progress readout.
  * Fixed crashes when minimizing the app during playback; playback now resumes
    cleanly at its position on restore.
  * Reworked search: search field in the header, type chips
    (Videos / Channels / Playlists) and swipeable results.
  * Settings (Region / Playback), an About page and Acknowledgements.

 -- IarChep <yarchepel@gmail.com>  Mon, 20 Jul 2026 02:16:45 +0400

meetube (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * First packaged release for the Nokia N9 (MeeGo Harmattan).
  * Home feed with categories, video page (comments, related, like/subscribe),
    sign-in (OAuth device code + QR), account page, channel page and search entry.
  * Self-contained: bundles OpenSSL 1.0.2, libpng12, libjpeg (IJG v6b), libwebp,
    a WebP Qt image plugin and a Mozilla CA bundle under /opt/meetube.

 -- IarChep <yarchepel@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 16:00:00 +0000
